      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Bruce Moreland</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:168px;\"><a href=\"http://www.thorstenczub.de/aegon.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/e1/Bruceaegon.gif\" width=\"166\" height=\"220\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Bruceaegon.gif\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Bruce Moreland <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Bruce Moreland</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist, former <a href=\"/Microsoft\" title=\"Microsoft\">Microsoft</a> employee and computer chess programmer, author of <a href=\"/Ferret\" title=\"Ferret\">Ferret</a>, one of the strongest chess engines at its time <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . Bruce published the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess program</a> <a href=\"/Gerbil\" title=\"Gerbil\">Gerbil</a> for educational purpose, and maintained a great computer chess programming site. The Gerbil site <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"#Topics\">programming topics</a> are archived by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos_.26_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos &amp; Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Post\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Post</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos_.26_Games\">Photos &amp; Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_Moreland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos &amp; Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:MorschCongratsMoreland.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"MorschCongratsMoreland.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/a1/MorschCongratsMoreland.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/WCCC_1999\" title=\"WCCC 1999\">WCCC 1999</a>: <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/Frans_Morsch\" title=\"Frans Morsch\">Frans Morsch</a>, <a href=\"/Matthias_W%C3%BCllenweber\" title=\"Matthias Wüllenweber\">Matthias Wüllenweber</a>, <a href=\"/Ferret\" title=\"Ferret\">Ferret</a> - <a href=\"/Fritz\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"WCCC 1999\"]\n[Site \"Paderborn, Germany\"]\n[Date \"1999.06.19\"]\n[Round \"7\"]\n[White \"Ferret\"]\n[Black \"Fritz\"]\n[Result \"1-0\"]\n\n1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 d6 3.d4 cxd4 4.Nxd4 Nf6 5.Nc3 a6 6.Be3 e5 7.Nb3 Be6\n8.f3 Be7 9.Qd2 Nbd7 10.g4 h6 11.h4 b5 12.O-O-O Nb6 13.Be2 b4 14.Nb1\nNfd7 15.Qxb4 d5 16.Qa5 d4 17.Bf2 Qc7 18.f4 Bxb3 19.axb3 Rc8 20.c3 Nc5\n21.Kc2 Nxe4 22.Bg1 f6 23.Bd3 Nc5 24.Bg6+ Kf8 25.fxe5 fxe5 26.b4 Ncd7\n27.Qa2 Qc4 28.Qxc4 Nxc4 29.Kb3 a5 30.Bf5 Ke8 31.bxa5 Nxa5+ 32.Ka2 Nc6\n33.cxd4 Nb4+ 34.Kb3 Rb8 35.Nc3 Nd3+ 36.Kc2 Nxb2 37.Ra1 Nc4 38.Ra7 Rd8\n39.Nb5 Nf8 40.Kc3 Nd6 41.Nc7+ Kf7 42.dxe5 Nxf5 43.gxf5 Kg8 44.Bd4 Rh7\n45.e6 h5 46.Kc4 Rc8 47.Kd3 Rd8 48.Ke4 g6 49.fxg6 Rxd4+ 50.Kxd4 Rg7\n51.Nd5 Nxe6+ 52.Ke5 Bd6+ 53.Kxd6 1-0\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_Moreland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Bruce Moreland (<b>1995</b>). various articles in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Reports\" title=\"Computer Chess Reports\">Computer Chess Reports Vol. 5 No. 3+4</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <i>Still more Chess Computer Memories</i>. pp. 34</dd>\n<dd> <i>Chess Life as Consumer Reports</i>. pp. 34</dd>\n<dd> <i>The Computer Strength and Weakness</i>. pp. 69</dd>\n<dd> <i>The Art of Tweaking</i>. pp. 69</dd>\n<dd> <i>The Value of Computers vs Computer Results</i>. pp. 71</dd>\n<dd> <i>Computer Problem Solving</i>. pp. 86</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Post\">Forum Post</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_Moreland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Post\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess/browse_frm/thread/8cc6428ab611f70e\">Repetition detection w/hash tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rec.games.chess</a>, August 14, 1993&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/g/rec.games.chess.computer/c/kecoM_YlyAM/m/NiCnP8wRgnQJ\">Computer chess books</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 05, 1997</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=40708\">Chess program similarity experiment</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Bionic_Impakt\" title=\"Bionic Impakt\">Bionic Impakt</a>, <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=189800\">Re: Ferret/Gerbil question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=275167\">Strength question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=291320\">Why I am not going to the Graz WCCC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_2003\" title=\"WCCC 2003\">WCCC 2003</a>, <a href=\"/Chrilly_Donninger\" title=\"Chrilly Donninger\">Chrilly Donninger</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3405#p17151\">Re: Mate scores in the hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bruce Moreland</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 04, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Score#MateScores\" title=\"Score\">Mate Scores</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<p><span id=\"Topics\"></span>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_Moreland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20071026090003/http://www.brucemo.com/compchess/programming/index.htm\">Bruce Moreland's Programming Topics</a> archived by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070607151211/www.brucemo.com/compchess/gerbil/index.htm\">Bruce Moreland's Gerbil</a> archived by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=12\">Bruce Moreland's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bruce_Moreland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.thorstenczub.de/aegon.html\">Aegon 1996-97</a> by <a href=\"/Thorsten_Czub\" title=\"Thorsten Czub\">Thorsten Czub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=35\">Ferret's ICGA Tournaments</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070607151211/www.brucemo.com/compchess/gerbil/index.htm\">Bruce Moreland's Gerbil</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20071026090003/http://www.brucemo.com/compchess/programming/index.htm\">Bruce Moreland's Programming Topics</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo from the no longer available <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a> site</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/round.php?tournament=8&amp;round=7&amp;id=10\">Paderborn 1999 - Chess - Round 7 - Game 10 (ICGA Tournaments)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301011310\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node coun